# Water temperature at the source is 25°C or higher. (Water below 25°C may be referred to as {{ill|cold springs|ja|冷泉|12=draft}} or {{ill|mineral springs|ja|鉱泉|1=Mineral spring|12=draft}}.) # Contains at least one of the following substances in the specified minimum quantities per kilogram: {|class=wikitable style="font-size:small" ! Substance !! Minimum content per kg |- | Dissolved solids (excluding gases) || style="text-align:right"| 1,000 mg |- | Free {{ill|carbon dioxide|ja|炭酸|12=draft}} (CO<sub>2</sub>) || style="text-align:right"| 250 mg |- | {{ill|Lithium ion|ja|リチウム|12=draft}} (Li<sup>+</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 1 mg |- | {{ill|Strontium ion|ja|ストロンチウム|12=draft}} (Sr<sup>++</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 10 mg |- | {{ill|Barium ion|ja|バリウム|12=draft}} (Ba<sup>++</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 5 mg |- | {{ill|Iron ions|ja|鉄|12=draft}} (Fe<sup>++</sup>, Fe<sup>+++</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 10 mg |- | Manganese ion (Mn<sup>++</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 10 mg |- | {{ill|Hydrogen ion|ja|水素|12=draft}} (H<sup>+</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 1 mg |- | {{ill|Bromine ion|ja|臭素|12=draft}} (Br<sup>-</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 5 mg |- | {{ill|Iodine ion|ja|沃素|12=draft}} (I<sup>-</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 1 mg |- | {{ill|Fluoride ion|ja|フッ素|12=draft}} (F<sup>-</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 2 mg |- | Hydrogen arsenate ion (HAsO<sub>4</sub><sup>--</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 1.3 mg |- | Metarsenous acid (HAsO<sub>2</sub>) || style="text-align:right"| 1 mg |- | Total {{ill|sulfur|ja|硫黄|12=draft}} (S) [HS<sup>-</sup>, S<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub><sup>--</sup>, H<sub>2</sub>S] || style="text-align:right"| 1 mg |- | {{ill|Metaboric acid|ja|ホウ酸|12=draft}} (HBO<sub>2</sub>) || style="text-align:right"| 5 mg |- | {{ill|Metasilicic acid|ja|ケイ酸|12=draft}} (H<sub>2</sub>SiO<sub>3</sub>) || style="text-align:right"| 50 mg |- | Sodium bicarbonate (NaHCO<sub>3</sub>) || style="text-align:right"| 340 mg |- | {{il