# Water temperature at the source is 25°C or higher. (Water below 25°C may be referred to as [[:en:Reizei|cold springs]] or [[:en:Mineral spring|Mineral spring]].) # Contains at least one of the following substances in the specified minimum quantities per kilogram: {|class=wikitable style="font-size:small" ! Substance !! Minimum content per kg |- | Dissolved solids (excluding gases) || style="text-align:right"| 1,000 mg |- | Free [[:en:Carbonic acid|carbon dioxide]] (CO<sub>2</sub>) || style="text-align:right"| 250 mg |- | [[:en:Lithium|Lithium ion]] (Li<sup>+</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 1 mg |- | [[:en:Strontium|Strontium ion]] (Sr<sup>++</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 10 mg |- | [[:en:Barium|Barium ion]] (Ba<sup>++</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 5 mg |- | [[:en:Iron|Iron ions]] (Fe<sup>++</sup>, Fe<sup>+++</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 10 mg |- | Manganese ion (Mn<sup>++</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 10 mg |- | [[:en:Hydrogen|Hydrogen ion]] (H<sup>+</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 1 mg |- | [[:en:Bromine|Bromine ion]] (Br<sup>-</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 5 mg |- | {{ill|Iodine ion|ja|沃素|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iodine ion|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ヨウ素|1=iodine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1103}} (I<sup>-</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 1 mg |- | [[:en:Fluorine|Fluoride ion]] (F<sup>-</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 2 mg |- | Hydrogen arsenate ion (HAsO<sub>4</sub><sup>--</sup>) || style="text-align:right"| 1.3 mg |- | Metarsenous acid (HAsO<sub>2</sub>) || style="text-align:right"| 1 mg |- | Total [[:en:Sulfur|sulfur]] (S) [HS<sup>-</sup>, S<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub><sup>--</sup>, H<sub>2</sub>S] || style="text-align:right"| 1 mg |- | [[:en:Boric acid|Metaboric acid]] (HBO<sub>2</sub>) || style="text-align:right"| 5 mg |- | [[:en:Silicic acid|Metasilicic acid]] (H<sub>2</sub>SiO<sub>3</sub>) || style="text-align:right"| 50 mg |- | Sodium bicarbonate (NaHCO<sub>3</sub>) || style=